Texts.Eng: Find the ^orange;artifact^reset; in ^green;the Dark Hunting Grounds^reset;
Hero fetches artifacts, saves universe. Right? Not in other reality. Why not? Go find first one. See if Kevin was there.
Kevin touched artifact, definitely, and...eww! He left it covered in raptor piss! Dirty stinker used it to etch 'Kevin was here' in the shiny. Hmm...have beacon with new signature though.
